                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/732</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the Assistant Secretary of State</hi> (<hi
                        rend="italic">White</hi>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-01-11">January 11,
                            1933</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Brazilian Ambassador telephoned to say that he was instructed by his
                    Government to express the thanks of the Brazilian Government for our support in
                    Lima of the Brazilian proposal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>F[<hi rend="smallcaps">rancis</hi>] W[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >hite</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
